Definition.WordDefinition:
empty-handed \empty-handed\ adj. having acquired or gained nothing; as, the returned from the negotiations empty-handed.
Syn: unrewarded. [WordNet 1.5]
2. carrying nothing in the hands. [WordNet 1.5]
